title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: When exporting data from the attached report, an exception is thrown.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table containing highlight/map should not result in an exception.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Attempt to export data from a table that contains highlight/map. 
3. Observe the thrown exception.
